Feature: Login

  Scenario Outline: Logowanie użytkowników
    Given  I go to login page
    When I type "<login>" as Username and "secret_sauce" as Password
    And  I click Login button
    Then I logged in
    Examples:
    |login|
    |standard_user|
    |locked_out_user|
    |problem_user   |
    |performance_glitch_user|
    |error_user             |
    |visual_user            |

    Scenario Outline: Użytkownik dodaje do koszyka wszystkie przedmioty
      Given I am logged in as "<login>"
      When I add all products
      Then I check out cart
      And I check "6" items
      Examples:
      |login|
      |standard_user|
      |problem_user   |
      |performance_glitch_user|
      |error_user             |
      |visual_user            |

      Scenario Outline: Użytkownik kończy zakupy
        Given I am logged in as "<login>" in shop
        And I have all products in card
        When Process order
        Then Finish order
        Examples:
        |login|
        |standard_user|
        |performance_glitch_user|
        |visual_user            |

